    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770390/extras/50a339535b55d908d705162373bc0110.avif?t=1749033329\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770390/extras/3bf8151bebc3f6d605df5f264f1e4013.poster.avif?t=1749033329\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770390/extras/3bf8151bebc3f6d605df5f264f1e4013.webm?t=1749033329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770390/extras/8c89e20341b4a589b4d14c30cfbc8c6b.avif?t=1749033329\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >横岛是个人生失败的杂志编辑，他爱上了自己的同事，有着一头乌黑秀发的美女一之濑叶月。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他一直努力在鼓起勇气想邀请对方约会，但是却一直没有机会实现这个愿望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而人算不如天算！叶月即将调动到海外分公司！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果他想要抓住最后的机会，就必须在对方调职之前竭尽所能！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏要素:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >浪漫恋情故事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >电子小说元素</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现代背景</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集叶月的喜好和厌恶内容等信息</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多重结局</p></li></ul>",
